These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing, gardening, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, superhero, drama, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball, badminton, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, tram, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8
 2. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
 5. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person driving the tram and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 9. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
13. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the helicopter##1
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles     | rock-climbing   | card-games | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | fantasy   | epic   | drama  |
| Sport         | volleyball  | badminton  | parkour  | swimming |
| Transport     | car    | helicopter | tram     | skateboard    |

