.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, soy-milk, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cucumber, kiwi, pomegranate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, gospel, disco, electronic
4 different pets are kept: snake, pony, hedgehog, turtle
 1. the fan of disco is between the owner of the snake and the fan of gospel##2
 2. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 4. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
 5. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
 6. the person eating pomegranate is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of funk is the owner of the pony##1
10. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
11. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the fan of disco##8
12. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
13. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the person eating cucumber##5
14. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
15. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
17. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the fan of gospel##8
18. the person eating cucumber is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
19. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | mirinda | soy-milk | almond-milk  | tea  |
| Food          | pomegranate     | cucumber | spinach | kiwi  |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco  | electronic | funk |
| Pet           | hedgehog | turtle | snake    | pony  |

