The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, romance, documentary, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, pop, salsa, funk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, golf, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
 5. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person watching documentary movies##8
 7. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
11. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the fan of pop##8
12. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | dancing    | puzzles   | singing | baking |
