.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, kiwi, lemon, artichoke
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, card-games, traveling, baking
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, journalist, coach, bartender
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cricket, climbing, soccer
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the fisherman##6
 2. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 3. the person eating artichoke is the coach##1
 4. the person eating kiwi is between the fisherman and the journalist##2
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person eating kiwi##8
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the bartender##1
10. the journalist is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person eating cherry##8
12. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
14. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
15. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
