10. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
11. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person watching family movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
13. the canadian is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
