.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, cola, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, entrepreneur, librarian, police-officer
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, turkish, american, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, trike, roller, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 2. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the police-officer##8
 3. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 5. the person driving the roller is the american##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the turkish##8
 7. the person drinking milk is not the russian##6
 8. the entrepreneur is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person drinking milk##7
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
11. the librarian is on the right of the photographer##1
12. the entrepreneur is not the japanese##6
13. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
14. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the entrepreneur##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | milk    | fanta   | cola        | coffee  |
| Job           | police-officer     | entrepreneur | photographer | librarian  |
| Nationality   | japanese | russian    | american   | turkish     |
| Transport     | jet-ski       | ship     | roller    | trike |

