 1. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 3. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 8. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
10. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the fan of country##8
11. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
12. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta   | almond-milk     | lemonade    | juice |
| Music-Genre   | house  | hip-hop      | punk     | country     |
| Sport         | badminton | water-polo  | rowing     | rugby  |
| Transport     | skateboard     | scooter | car | train     |

