.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, woodworking, dancing, singing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, jazz, hip-hop, country
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, japanese, egyptian, indian
 1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the indian##1
 2. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of jazz##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the left of the fan of disco##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 9. the japanese is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
10. the fan of hip-hop is not the argentine##6
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
12. the indian is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the fan of country is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
14. the argentine is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | tea      | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk | water        |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking   | card-games   | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | country    | jazz   | hip-hop    | disco      |
| Nationality   | japanese   | indian | egyptian   | argentine    |

