The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, car, skateboard
 1. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 2. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the security-guard##8
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking water##1
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
 6. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking cola##1
 7. the project-manager is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
 8. the analyst is on the far right##1
 9. the security-guard is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
12. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
13. the person driving the car is not to the left of the project-manager##8

