The people use 4 different means of transport: train, scooter, trike, boat
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 2. the librarian is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the librarian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8
 5. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
 6. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 8. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the doctor##8
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
10. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the security-guard##7
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
