.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, writing, traveling, card-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, engineer, journalist, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, drama, scientific, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, metal, folk, salsa
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the left of the dancer##8
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 3. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
 4. the writer is the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the journalist##6
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
 7. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the journalist##8
 8. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
 9. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
10. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
11. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the journalist and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
13. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | card-games    | traveling   | cooking   | writing |
| Job           | dancer | engineer    | journalist | writer    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific   | fantasy | drama     | sports    |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | folk      | metal         | salsa     |

 